     <div id="comment-840">

      <img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d0bdb5db28d32f2454db443fd7e75e89?s=48&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2F1.gravatar.com%2Favatar%2Fad516503a11cd5ca435acc9bb6523536%3Fs%3D48&amp;r=X' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />
      <div class="comment-author">
	
         <cite class="fn">Don Stark</cite> | <span class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://equivocality.com/2006/06/11/review-homestar-21st-century-home-planetarium/#comment-840">#</a></span>

