      <p>This seems like a pretty cool toy — I espe­cially like the idea of a sleep timer :) One of the sev­eral plea­sures of camp­ing away from all the light pol­lu­tion is to be able to get lost in the vast dis­tances and time that the stars rep­re­sent. I’d be impressed if this could instill even some of the feel­ing that I get from the expe­ri­ence of camp­ing out on a clear night…</p>

